title: Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile"
description: The profile outline depicts a flat forehead, upturned nose, closed lips, and rounded, upraised chin. The chin line extends downward into the diagonal line of the neck as well as upward toward the ear (not visible). The eye is half-closed under a straight brow. A fringe of curly hair frames the face.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile".
24 x 21.7 cm (9 1/2 x 8 1/2 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-118.
